e,parent_pod,child_pod,operation_name,status_code,status_message,occurrence_count\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,frontend-0,frontend-0,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,4,context deadline exceeded,出现次数:552\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,4,context deadline exceeded,出现次数:410\naiops-k8s-01,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,4,context deadline exceeded,出现次数:397\n", "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-17T18:10:04Z to 2025-06-17T18:29:04Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-17 18:10:04+00:00 to 2025-06-17 18:29:04+00:00"}, "trace_data_collected": true, "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的监控数据，我现在进行全面的异常调用链扫描分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"frontend->adservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"AdService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"AdService调用延迟从正常5.5秒激增至500秒（延迟倍数90倍），出现大量'context deadline exceeded'错误（共1359次）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"PaymentService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PaymentService调用延迟从正常13.9秒增至36秒（延迟倍数2.6倍），影响checkout流程\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CartService相关操作延迟显著增加：GetCart从8.2秒增至16.1秒，EmptyCart从18.5秒增至27.7秒\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis操作HGET延迟从1.7秒增至7.6秒（延迟倍数4.4倍），影响CartService性能\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"EmailService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"EmailService调用延迟从0.67秒增至2.5秒（延迟倍数3.7倍），影响订单确认流程\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n1. **最严重的异常**：AdService服务完全不可用，延迟激增90倍，出现大量超时错误，这可能是系统故障的根因。\n\n2. **支付系统影响**：PaymentService延迟增加2.6倍，可能影响用户结账体验。\n\n3. **购物车服务问题**：CartService及其依赖的Redis存储都出现显著延迟，影响购物车操作。\n\n4. **推荐服务异常**：RecommendationService调用ProductCatalogService的延迟也出现异常波动。\n\n5. **错误传播路径**：AdService的故障可能通过前端服务传播，影响整个系统的用户体验。\n\n建议进一步深入分析AdService的具体故障原因，以及检查PaymentService和CartService的依赖关系。", "log_analysis_findings": "### 初始扫描结果\n\n根据获取的日志数据，以下是分析结果：\n\n#### 检测到的关键错误关键词 (`detected_log_keys`):\n- `DeadlineExceeded`\n- `context deadline exceeded`\n- `failed to retrieve ads`\n\n#### 假设 (`hypotheses`):\n1. **异常组件**: `frontend`\n   - **原因**: 多个 `frontend` 实例报告了与广告服务 (`ads`) 的 RPC 调用超时 (`DeadlineExceeded`)，表明广告服务可能无法及时响应或不可用。\n   - **证据**: 日志中频繁出现 `failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded`。\n\n2. **异常组件**: `ads` (广告服务)\n   - **原因**: 所有错误日志均指向 `frontend` 调用 `ads` 服务时超时，可能是 `ads` 服务负载过高或存在性能问题。\n   - **证据**: 日志中多次提到 `failed to retrieve ads` 和 `context deadline exceeded`。\n\n### 输出 JSON\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"DeadlineExceeded\", \"context deadline exceeded\", \"failed to retrieve ads\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"RPC calls to ads service timed out (DeadlineExceeded)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ads\",\n      \"reason\": \"Potential performance issues or unavailability causing RPC timeouts (DeadlineExceeded)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to retrieve ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 下一步建议\n1. **深入调查 `ads` 服务**: 检查 `ads` 服务的日志和监控数据，确认是否存在性能瓶颈或故障。\n2. **检查网络延迟**: 确认 `frontend` 与 `ads` 之间的网络连接是否正常。\n3. **扩展 `ads` 服务资源**: 如果 `ads` 服务负载过高，考虑增加实例或优化资源分配。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的监控数据，我已经完成了对故障时间段 2025-06-17T18:10:04Z 至 2025-06-17T18:29:04Z 的全面扫描分析。以下是发现的主要异常情况：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"pod_processes\", \"region_pending\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"request\", \"response\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存资源严重不足，node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes下降44.1%，node_memory_usage_rate上升38.35%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes从8.65GB降至4.87GB，node_memory_usage_rate从47.54%升至70.09%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend服务\",\n      \"reason\": \"前端服务响应时间显著恶化，rrt_max和rrt指标大幅上升\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0的rrt_max从238895升至620221(上升159.7%)，frontend-2的rrt从12163.8升至38541.94(上升216.9%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"TiDB存储引擎出现region_pending队列积压，上升23.48%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"region_pending从10460.5升至13244，表明数据库处理能力下降\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Redis Pod的pod_processes指标出现异常变化，p99值下降33.33%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_processes的p99值从2.0降至1.0，可能存在进程重启或异常\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"广告服务请求量和响应量异常波动，request和response指标变化显著\",\n      \"evidence\": \"request从298.5降至107(下降64.2%)，response从300降至98(下降67.3%)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**主要发现总结：**\n\n1. **节点级问题**：aiops-k8s-04节点内存严重不足，可能是系统故障的主要根源\n2. **服务性能问题**：frontend服务响应时间大幅恶化，多个实例受影响\n3. **数据库问题**：TiDB存储引擎出现处理积压\n4. **Pod生命周期异常**：Redis Pod可能存在重启或进程异常\n5. **服务流量异常**：adservice请求响应模式异常\n\n这些发现为后续深入分析提供了明确的线索方向。"}
